name: Experiment Or Die #53
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. One of my favorite bands from my time in Atlanta and in general is Mastodon. Ive seen them several times but this pic was from the Tabernacle in 2011 and they've only gotten better. How long til we see huge bands like that in the crypto space? Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
